#    [ ] Add VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY
#
# ✅ Step 3: Payment Processing
#    [ ] Set up Stripe account
#    [ ] Get Stripe API keys
#    [ ] Add STRIPE_SECRET_KEY and VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
